eNCA’s Siphamandla Goge reports. Courtesy #DStv403 KWANYUSWA, KwaZulu-Natal - Disgraced ANC executive member, Zweli Mkhize says the party should not adopt the Animal Farm approach when implementing its resolutions on fighting corruption. The former health minister left government under the cloud of the Digital Vibes scandal. Mkhize spoke in KwaNyuswa, where he’s been endorsed for the party’s top job. eNCA’s Siphamandla Goge shares more details in the video above.